(17, 1, '2017-08-21 17:28:36', '2017-08-21 17:28:36', 'Like many UK grown developers, after getting my eager little hands on a ZX Spectrum as a boy, I have been coding with many of the different technologies we have enjoyed over the years. After these early app and game attempts as a chil, I soon started to implement more serious JavaScript within the audio technology domain through my studies. This in turn lead me to development of websites within a professional context and the journey continues to roll on with the same childish enthusiam.\r\n\r\nFront-End Technologies:\r\n\r\nThese days it''s full-stack development with a 70/30 slat to front-end with specialsm including:\r\n\r\n(HTML 5 badge)\r\n(CSS 3 badge)\r\n(JS badge)\r\n(Response Web Design Badge)\r\n\r\nBack-End Technologies:\r\n\r\n(Grunt badge)\r\n(Express badge)\r\n(Node badge)\r\n(Sass badge)\r\n(PHP badge)', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-08-21 17:28:36', '2017-08-21 17:28:36', '', 2, 'http://localhost/fifthmorrison/?p=17', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
